How this works

Wheel Badge system:
1. 1. - Excited Rider
2. 10 -  Happy Commuter
3. 30 -  Safety Officer
4. 60 - Railroad Engineer
5. 90 - Master Conductor status
Every 30 ride = 6 free ride 
Starting after first status - sponsor rewards apply.
Wheels as “stars”

Resets every 3 months.

New Badges for every “season”

Sponsor specific surveys / rewards
30% off next beer coupons, etc

